doc.field: William Morris to: Kenworthy, [John Coleman] Contents: six letters, one undated. Concern trips by Morris to Liverpool, where Kenworthy apparently lived, possible meetings in London, and [upon Kenworthy's return from a trip to America] Morris' aversion to the idea of traveling to America.
